powhiri
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a formal Maori welcoming ceremony on a marae or elsewhere.
Origin:Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:also pohiri
Pronunciation:
Notes:
